data.description: Beautifully maintained, like new 3BR/2BA home in Ruskin.  With an open and spacious floor plan, this home offers plenty of room for comfortable living and entertaining.  The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and an ample breakfast bar for meal prep space or additional seating.  The bedrooms are generously sized, with the primary bedroom having an ensuite bathroom with large shower and walk in closet!  Enjoy your fenced backyard with a gorgeous pond view and NO backyard neighbors!  The Spencer Creek Community offers plenty of amenities including a community pool, playground, basketball court and community mailboxes.   Close to shopping, restaurants and some of the best beaches our area has to offer! *This home can be purchased with an assumable mortgage with an interest rate of 2.75%*
